title: How to Do Your Own Cute Nails
creator: BEAUTY LINX

extendedInfo.description: All you wanted to know about glamorizing your nails, in one place!Make your nails look fabulous without going to the salon!- Over 250 video tutorials that show you how to beautify your nails- Application is updated daily with new useful videos- Great number of tips and tricks for doing creative nail designs- Guidance about nail care- Advices to keep your fingernails healthy, strong and gorgeousThis app will help you learn how to create a large number of interesting and cute nail designs on your own, without going to the salon. It has over 250 videos which demonstrate what should be done to make certain nail design, and the number of videos is increased every day.With advice from this beauty application you will learn how to give yourself a true spa treatment without spending tons of money! Watch videos in which technicians reviewed lots of polishes and kits and choose a cheap or expensive one, whichever suits your pocket. Listen carefully their tips and follow their instructions for beginners and learn in no time to create lovely French manicure! With a bit of practice, youâll become an expert in creating more demanding nailart, adding flowers and other decorations. But if youâre already an artist and you think these designs are too simple, you can use this app to find ideas and inspiration. Download How to Do Your Own âCute Nailsâ and learn to paint lots of Christmas inspired motifs on your fingernails. No matter if you prefer working with gel or acrylic, youâll certainly find something that fit your taste and fashion style.Creating an app takes time and money, In order to keep creating great (and free) apps, we are using a new search service to monetize our apps. With this service we are able to create more great apps for you girls. This option bundles a few search points (icon, bookmark and homepage) for you to use. You can erase these easily and with no effect to our app. You can delete the search shortcuts easily (Drag & Drop to the garbage). Thanks. This free app is ad supported and may contain ads in the notification tray. This app offers numerous video tutorials for doing many different manicure styles and nailart designs in one place.Need some nail art inspiration? Get ready for some manicure magic as we bring you the hottest nail designs from celebrities, beauty brands and the catwalks.
